com.javafst

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.javafst.State
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImmutableState

    public class State
extends java.lang.Object
    The fst's mutable state implementation.

    Holds its outgoing Arc objects in an ArrayList allowing additions/deletions.
